data.description: Timber Creek beauty alert! New floors throughout, new ROOF, completely renovated kitchen, 3 car garage, massive yard with pond views, fresh landscaping, and so much more. Step inside to your formal dining room up front. Continue on to your open kitchen overlooking your massive family room. Kitchen complete with gorgeous Quartz counters, custom white cabinets, and more. Head upstairs to a massive loft, perfect for office space or an entertainment room. Oversized master bedroom is completely private and tucked away with gorgeous backyard views. Laundry room is spacious with cabinet space and open shelving. Backyard is fully fenced and offers an adorable pavered area, perfect for late night fire pit sessions. Timbercreek is centrally located with easy access to 95 for travel to Jax or Kings Bay, and an easy drive to Amelia Island Beaches. NO CDD, this community offers a gorgeous clubhouse, pool, basketball courts, playground and more. See it today before she's snagged!
